  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.8.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 2.8.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.8.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>January 24, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.lifecycle:lifecycle-*:2.8.0-alpha01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/09469f458ee5c8201480dab80e18c923c531db9e..51191bc12f96f233fc08995e1b4e8ff8b88bc7ce/lifecycle\">Version 2.8.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ViewModel</code> now supports adding <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">Closeable</code> objects with a <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">key</code> that allows retrieving them via <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">getCloseable()</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I3cf63385f043090daa9dd45cbe74464b36ca47a9\">I3cf63</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_27_2\" data-text=\"Version 2.7\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.7</h2>",
